Name: Epic Helicopter
About the game: Epic Helicopter is an arcade game. Take control of your helicopter and reach the finish line without hitting any obstacle in 2.5 d and 3d scenes. Reach the goal avoiding different static and interpolated constructions in this game with spectacular natural environments.
